title: NRBQ - discography
description: One of the best lesser known bands ever, blending elements of Beatlesque pop, rockabilly, free jazz, and more into a unique musical stew. Not known for cohesive albums, they nonetheless released a staggering amount of quality work spread out over the dozens of cds I have stuffed into this, my 1st torrent upload. Most of this was ripped by me, various bitrates. I hope somebody finds it useful, and any feedback would be appreciated.
